\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\norm f_{r,s} & <\infty
\end{align*}

\end_inset

This space is an infinite-dimensional vector space.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

On a normed space 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(E,\norm .\right)$
\end_inset

, the topology is given by the open sets.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega\subseteq E$
\end_inset

