 Then 
\begin_inset Formula $fT$
\end_inset

 is a 
\emph on
continuous
\emph default
 linear functional on 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{S}\left(\mathbb{R}^{n}\right)$
\end_inset

, in other words 
\begin_inset Formula $fT\in\mathcal{S}^{*}\left(\mathbb{R}^{n}\right)$
\end_inset

