So we have the following correspondence:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
-\ii x^{j} & \leftrightarrow\frac{\partial}{\partial p^{j}}\\
-\ii\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{j}} & \leftrightarrow p^{j}
