\begin_inset Formula $\left(M,g\right)$
\end_inset

.
 Polar coordinates give a special chart on 
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega\subseteq M$
\end_inset

 with 
\begin_inset Formula $0\not\in\Omega$
\end_inset

.
 The we can calculate 
\begin_inset Formula $\upDelta=\LBO$
\end_inset

