 & \qquad+\Gamma'\left(\frac{\norm y}{R}\norm{x-\tilde{y}}\right)\frac{\norm y}{R}\upDelta\norm{x-\tilde{y}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

We know:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
